description: The MSCI EM Latin America Low Carbon SRI Selection Capped Index aims to reflect the performance of the following market: Large and mid-cap companies from Latin American Emerging Markets with high ESG characteristics and low carbon exposures, relative to their peers Reviewed on a quarterly basis Additional information on the index, selection and weighting methodology is available at https://www.msci.com
name: Xtrackers MSCI EM Latin America ESG Swap UCITS ETF 1C
